column5: The interior of a modern shopping area with a unique bamboo structure resembling a large mushroom or umbrella. There are various clothing items displayed on wooden shelves. The ceiling has a sleek, striped design, and mannequins are dressed in colorful outfits.
column6: Loob ng isang modernong pamilihan na may kakaibang istrukturang kawayan na kahawig ng malaking kabute o payong. May iba't ibang damit na nakadisplay sa mga kahoy na istante. Ang kisame ay may makinis na disenyo na may guhit, at ang mga manikin na nakasuot ng makukulay na damit.

column5: The entrance of a Jollibee restaurant. There is a statue of the Jollibee mascot outside, and several people are seated inside eating. The interior is brightly lit, and the wall features the Jollibee logo and images of the mascot in different dance poses.
column6: Pasukan ng isang Jollibee restaurant. May estatwa ng Jollibee mascot sa labas, at may ilang tao na nakaupo sa loob at kumakain. Ang loob ay maliwanag at ang dingding ay may logo ng Jollibee at mga imahe ng mascot sa iba't ibang yugto ng sayaw.

column5: A vineyard with rows of grapevines bearing clusters of green grapes. The vines are supported by a trellis system.
column6: Ubasan na may mga hanay ng mga kumpol ng berdeng ubas. Ang mga puno ng ubas ay sinusuportahan ng isang trellis system.

column5: A table with various Filipino dishes. In the foreground, there is a bowl of kare-kare, a Filipino stew with a peanut sauce, containing meat, eggplant, and green beans. In the background, there is a plate with vigan longanisa, a type of sausage, and vegetable stir-fry.
column6: Mesa na may iba't ibang putaheng Pilipino. Sa harapan, mayroong mangkok ng kare-kare, isang ulam na may sarsa ng mani, na may laman na karne, talong, at sitaw. Sa likuran, may plato na may longanisang vigan at ginisang gulay.

column5: A plate with slices of roasted meat, commonly called "lechon," and a rolled crepe filled with vegetables also known as fresh lumpia.
column6: Isang plato na may mga hiwa ng lechon at isang piraso ng fresh lumpia.

column5: A dog baithing in a river surrounded by mangrove trees with small boats in the background.
column6: Isang aso na naliligo sa ilog na napapaligiliran ng mga puno ng bakawan. May maliliit na bangka sa likuran.

column5: An open space covered by a roof made of bamboo with trees surround the area.
column6: Isang espasyo na natatakpan ng bubong na gawa sa kawayan at napapalibutan ng mga puno.
